metadata.name: NGT 01
metadata.description:
Drive, Drift and Explore the Night.

NIGHT DRIFT is a collection of limited edition and one-of-a-kind exclusive NFTs generated with the help of the AI entity DALL-E. 

This specially curated collection of 1:1 Artworks is inspired by the dreamy sound of Night Drive Music, that uses themes of phonk and drifting music.

Conceptualizing a unique visual experience that transcends space and time, it aims to reacteate the moodines of the driving alone at night.
